"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"The greatest function of movies is the exercise ground of life. In \\\"Life Creativity Lesson\\\", it is written that you can learn by playing movie roles. Choose 1-2 characters to play in a movie and think about how I want to live my life from his point of view. This way you can experience hundreds of different lives, then your soul will increase a lot of different experiences, and the width of your life will increase.\\n\\n\\nIf you carefully write down your experience of using your new identity in a notebook after watching a movie, practice it a few more times. When you have a higher view, a broader perspective, then when you look back at this thing you are angry and aggrieved about now, your experience will be different.\\n\\n\\nYou can ask yourself.\\nIf I were a screenwriter, how do I make the plot more dramatic and easier to immerse myself in? Is there a logical gap in the plot, and does the audience believe it when they see it?\\n\\n\\nIf I am the protagonist, how do I control my life and turn my fate around?\\nIf I were the director, how would I make the film better, and what aspects need to be improved?\",\"timestamp\":1636906895,\"title\":\"How to watch movies more efficiently?\"},\"digest\":\"oKJU25eHs3ick0FMCvki4_u3t0pUYTpE6uMm7MnlOyI\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x71213a9C9504E406d3242436A4bf69c6bfE74461\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"eaRiLDH82PZsNbEaMezG5WyMkwxxDMbpIQdaT14De4E\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"vUJEvtR7mjqkwKr3jsUt_OMmk3iUBnb7Ab4SdzFmurw\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"8ZVqT-Grnm1T904xXVqPmJ6XrKogfhsNv6lP0zG-RNKbyL7uIV1Rq7RuAE0NNhMiENnqRku2lXEExbdrwRMJxw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x0097975467da54f28da985dce051aefef1640b785ed2828a3984ba9c14bbc61b3f21437fdf9b28eb83cb294d7a9b0d0f1fc25dc0e76fb65568523db85ab73fa01c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\